{"tid":1090741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6÷2（1+2）＝？","createTime":"2019-04-03T16:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T18:39:29.000Z","uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"52583fcc25c665f901247d8171a311adbbc561ba","tid":1090741,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:26:30.000Z","msg":"點解計到1係錯呢？<br />\n<br />\n乘同除邊個計先唔係一樣嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2X6/3=4<br />\n2x6=12<br />\n12/3=4<br />\n<br />\n2x6/3<br />\n6/3=2<br />\n2x2=4<br />\n<br />\n求解！<br />\n<br />\n利申，家姐佢讀緊小學，佢畀同學仔問，佢唔識所以問做阿妹嘅我。<br />\n再利申：我剛讀完中一"},{"pid":"d41ffac1d4fa6da869e9d83ebabc3f0fe26a7d31","tid":1090741,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:27:23.000Z","msg":"真心嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d69c826713bfe180ddbc8a05820fd7a09113a21","tid":1090741,"uid":5460,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"仲細咩 除號已經冇乜人用 <br />\n因為好易混淆"},{"pid":"7f61a4e4749423dce62c3e85166c4c69fe286840","tid":1090741,"uid":39668,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"6&divide;<span style=\"color: red;\">2（1+2）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢種乘法只可以用係代數上<br />\n就算比你乘 條式都係<br />\n6&divide;2x(1+2)<br />\n6&divide;2x3<br />\n3x3<br />\n9<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"733db97517b68462e0cfba5e213cfaaa8d48e807","tid":1090741,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"7f61a4e4749423dce62c3e85166c4c69fe286840","tid":1090741,"uid":39668,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"6&divide;<span style=\"color: red;\">2（1+2）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢種乘法只可以用係代數上<br />\n就算比你乘 條式都係<br />\n6&divide;2x(1+2)<br />\n6&divide;2x3<br />\n3x3<br />\n9<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"呢個我明呀！<br />\n但去到6/2x3呢到有問題<br />\n<br />\n除同乘唔係邊個先邊個後都係一樣嘅咩？"},{"pid":"901a19c20b63ba14cb3078f02036420e567f9c08","t