,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:47:33.000Z","msg":"6/2（1+2）<br />\n=4（6）<br />\n=25<br />\n唔知啱唔啱呢姐姐<br />\n<br />\n利申：K3上晝班"},{"pid":"a51e366755190440ab7b55e6724a39fc5b1e2061","tid":1090741,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:51:14.000Z","msg":"6&divide;2x=?"},{"pid":"522cd7716e9e8658c283fec83836c606aac928b8","tid":1090741,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"733db97517b68462e0cfba5e213cfaaa8d48e807","tid":1090741,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"7f61a4e4749423dce62c3e85166c4c69fe286840","tid":1090741,"uid":39668,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"6&divide;<span style=\"color: red;\">2（1+2）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢種乘法只可以用係代數上<br />\n就算比你乘 條式都係<br />\n6&divide;2x(1+2)<br />\n6&divide;2x3<br />\n3x3<br />\n9<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"呢個我明呀！<br />\n但去到6/2x3呢到有問題<br />\n<br />\n除同乘唔係邊個先邊個後都係一樣嘅咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"例子<br />\n1/2*3<br />\n你計1/2先再*3 不等於 2*3先再用1除"},{"pid":"ca1f2fc4d9f8660050fb10d213566b8fd6afdb23","tid":1090741,"uid":238399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:14:13.000Z","msg":"感覺重點唔係條數，重點係距家姐讀小學，而距讀完中一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdbe927206dae60cf2b4bee9d2fa74f24a0873f","tid":1090741,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"我比較想知 你家姐係點樣嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大過你都可以讀小學 你就讀中學"},{"pid":"a85e6da7768114de7e0e1ad113ec8fb0867a3998","tid":1090741,"uid":85682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:27:21.000Z","msg":"除x = 乘1/x<br />\n根本唔存在先算乘後除嘅次序，因為佢哋係同一樣operator, 按照次序計算就啱"},{"pid":"1acf51434d4dfa99645091c00f1425567ca6b7a8","tid":1090741,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"邊個同你講乘除唔洗分先後次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d223c7dbb91154fdc748686910f501da5832982","tid":1090741,"uid":22165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"733db97517b68462e0cfba5e213cfaaa8d48e807","tid":1090741,"uid":9997,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"7f61a4e4749423dce62c3e85166c4c69fe286840","tid":1090741,"uid":39668,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:33:36.000Z","msg":"6&divide;<span style=\"color: red;\">2（1+2）</span><br />\n<br />\n呢種乘法只可以用係代數上<br />\n就算比你乘 條式都係<br />\n6&divide;2x(1+2)<br />\n6&divide;2x3<br />\n3x3<br />\n9<br />\n<br />\n完"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"呢個我明呀！<br />\n但去到6/2x3呢到有問題<br />\n<br />\n除同乘唔係邊個先邊個後都係一樣嘅咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"屌仲以為自己好撚醒搵到破綻<br />\n係一樣呀 6乘3先同除2先都得<br />\n如果你話2乘3 係你根本唔明數學原理 不學無術/好撚蠢"},{"pid":"d5e6f196240ed020bf26a0b8a19af6f9509d3740","tid":1090741,"uid":238399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1acf51434d4dfa99645091c00f1425567ca6b7a8","tid":1090741,"uid":181156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:30:45.000Z","msg":"邊個同你講乘除唔洗分先後次序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJ11ZKA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJ11ZKA.png&h=c972afd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問你，先乘同先除有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27127a0411dd35e65fc485f3dedef3d1aaa7e48d","tid":1090741,"uid":156609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"從嚴格意義上來說 6&divide;2(1+2)這個表達式本身就是不規範，或者錯誤的。因為乘號「x」通常在有字母的式子中才有可能省略，而在純數字的式子中，乘號是不允許省略的。<br />\n所以當以代數既邏輯思考時,<br />\nassume 6&divide;2x=y  and x=x1+x2<br />\nwhen x1 =1 and x2 = 2,<br />\n6&divide;[2x(1+2)]=y<br />\ny= 6&divide;6<br />\ny=1<br />\n不過本來條問題寫法就有問題，所以已經無話邊個答案先係正確。"},{"pid":"9e489f6c5cc36ed4d90e63727a1ae14bd67605d8","tid":1090741,"uid":245399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T18:39:29.000Z","msg":"其實數式就好似語言咁，好多時為咗方便會簡化咗佢，有時係會令人誤會。<br />\n<br />\n6&divide;2(1+2) 可以理解為 6&divide;2&times;(1+2) 或 6&divide;( 2(1+2) )，前者懶寫乘號，後者懶寫括號。不過通常應該當係前者。<br />\n<br />\n舉例說明，通常冇誤會嘅簡寫：<br />\nsin2x 一般黎講係想表達 sin(2x) ，但係你可以理解為 sin(2) x 咁。<br />\n<br />\n又或者好多個數連加，我地通常唔寫括號：<br />\nA+B+C+D 本身應該寫成 ((A+B)+C)+D ，但全部都係加，點計都唔會錯，就咪鬼寫咁多括號啦，睇到眼都花。<br />\n<br />\n又或者積分式通常會咁寫：<br />\n&int; ax+b dx 本身應該寫做 &int; ( ax+b ) dx ，但通常都係 &int; 同 dx 夾住個 Function，唔會誤會。<br />\n<br />\n結論係：當有好多人對 6&divide;2(1+2) 嘅理解有分歧，就唔應該咁寫。<br />\n<br />\n利申：數學撚"}]}